data.title: JP. RAFFARIN AND KISHORE MAHBUBANI'S DIALOGUE
data.meta_description: As part of the Futuroscope Forum 2021 edition “Finding balance in an unstable world”, Jean-Pierre RAFFARIN, Former Prime Minister and President of the Fondation Prospective et Innovation spoke with Prof.Kishore MAHBUBANI, Singaporean Diplomat, about his latest book “Has China Won? The Chinese Challenge to American Primacy” (Saint Simon Editions, ISBN-10 : 2374350282) and his views on the US-China relationship. Find here the book review of “Has China Won? The Chinese Challenge to American Primacy“.
data.text:
As part of the Futuroscope Forum 2021 edition “Finding balance in an unstable world”, Jean-Pierre RAFFARIN, Former Prime Minister and President of the Fondation Prospective et Innovation spoke with Prof.Kishore MAHBUBANI, Singaporean Diplomat, about his latest book “Has China Won? The Chinese Challenge to American Primacy” (Saint Simon Editions, ISBN-10 : 2374350282) and his views on the US-China relationship.

Find here the book review of “Has China Won? The Chinese Challenge to American Primacy“.
